OL,3,CSurge in anti-Jewish hatred hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high fueled by Middle East
OL,5,Cconflict
OL,7,FThe conflict in the Middle East has
OL,8,Ffueled a shocking rise in antisemitic
OL,9,Fhate crime with the majority of cases
OL,10,Fin London.
OL,12,FAccording to a Jewish charity there
OL,13,Fwere more than 4,103 recorded anti-
OL,14,FJewish hate crimes last year in the UK
OL,15,Fof which 2,410 were in the capital.
OL,17,FDave Rich from the Community Security
OL,18,FTrust said he's seen this kind of
OL,19,Fextremism before, but his time it
OL,20,F"felt different".
