OL,3,CSurge in anti-Jewish hatred hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high fueled by Middle East
OL,5,Cconflict
OL,7,F"When the Hamas terror attack began in
OL,8,FIsrael we knew there would be a surge
OL,9,Fin anti-Jewish hatred in this country
OL,10,Fbecause we've seen it so many times
OL,11,Fbefore. But I think the scale of it is
OL,12,Freally shocking," Dave Rich said.
OL,14,F"The size of the increase so much
OL,15,Fhigher than any other previous annual
OL,16,Ftotal. The fact that we've seen
OL,17,Fincidents in every single part of the
OL,18,FUnited Kingdom, I think it feels for a
OL,19,Flot of British Jews, like something
OL,20,Freally changed on the 7th of October.
