OL,5,Cconflict
OL,7,F"Of course, we've seen anti-Semitism
OL,8,Fbefore. We've seen this kind of
OL,9,Fextremism before. But it feels
OL,10,Fdifferent," he added.
OL,12,FDave said he had seen a tripling of
OL,13,Fincidents in schools, a similar
OL,14,Fincrease in universities and
OL,15,Fcomplaints from workplaces. "We've
OL,16,Fseen the highest ever increase in
OL,17,Fonline anti-Semitism," he explained.
