OL,7,FAsked if Jewish people had changed
OL,8,Ftheir day-to-day behaviour to avoid
OL,9,Fbeing targeted, he said: "I think a
OL,10,Flot of Jewish people are very worried
OL,11,Fabout what this means for the future
OL,12,Fin a very practical sense, whether it
OL,13,Fis safe to leave their home and show
OL,14,Fthat they are visibly Jewish or if
OL,15,Fthey have to change their behavior.
OL,17,F"I think there's an inner strength in
OL,18,Fthe community to get through this as
OL,19,Fwell.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
