OL,7,F"But there's also a lot of anger that
OL,8,Fthis is even happening in the first
OL,9,Fplace. You know, Britain over the
OL,10,Fyears has become a country where it's
OL,11,Fbeen a really good place to be Jewish.
OL,13,F"And this feels like it's not the
OL,14,FBritain that we have come to know.
OL,15,FWhen people are asking where this is
OL,16,Fcoming from and where it's heading."
