OL,7,FDave said the highest number of anti-
OL,8,FSemitic incidents was in London
OL,9,Fbecause the city had the largest
OL,10,FJewish community in the UK.JDave said:
OL,11,F"London is a place that prides itself
OL,12,Fon its diversity. The people of every
OL,13,Fbackground and origin can come here
OL,14,Fand have a great life, and that's part
OL,15,Fof our values. Since 7th October, the
OL,16,FJewish community in London has felt
OL,17,Flike we're not part of that, we can't
OL,18,Fenjoy that anymore.
